| Set the original source file for the manual.

Set Create$Source <Obey$Dir>.Source
Set Create$Sprite <Obey$Dir>.ManSprite

| Set the destination for the text manual.

Set Create$TX$Dest <Obey$Dir>.^.!IcnClpBrd.!Help

| Set the destination and intermediate files for the StrongHelp manual.

Set Create$SH$Dest ADFS::Iyonix.$.Public.Programming.Accounts.!CashBook.Resources.UK.CashBook
Set Create$SH$Inter ADFS::Iyonix.$.Public.Programming.Accounts.Manual.SHInter

| Set the destination for the DDF output.

Set Create$WP$Dest ADFS::Iyonix.$.Public.Programming.Accounts.Manual.DDF

| Delete the text manual and recreate it.

IfThere <Create$TX$Dest> Then Delete <Create$TX$Dest>
Do "TextMan <Create$Source> <Create$TX$Dest>"

| Delete the StrongHelp intermediate file and recreate it.

|IfThere <Create$SH$Inter> Then Wipe <Create$SH$Inter> ~CR
|CDir <Create$SH$Inter>
|Do "StrongMan <Create$Source> <Create$SH$Inter>"

| Delete the real StrongHelp manual and recreate it.

|IfThere <Create$SH$Dest> Then Delete <Create$SH$Dest>
|StrongCreate <Create$SH$Dest>

|Repeat Copy <Create$SH$Inter> "<Create$SH$Dest>.* ~C" -verbose
|Repeat SetType <Create$SH$Dest> FFF -verbose

|Copy <Create$Sprite> <Create$SH$Dest>.Sprites ~C

|<StrongHelp$Dir>.Utilities.CleanCopy <Create$SH$Dest>

| Delete the intermediate files.

|IfThere <Create$SH$Inter> Then Wipe <Create$SH$Inter> ~CR

| Delete the DDF output and recreate it.

|IfThere <Create$WP$Dest> Then Delete <Create$WP$Dest>
|Do "DDFMan <Create$Source> <Create$WP$Dest>"
|SetType <Create$WP$Dest> 707

| Tidy up and end.

UnSet Create$Source
Unset Create$Sprite

UnSet Create$SH$Dest
UnSet Create$SH$Inter

UnSet Create$TX$Dest

Unset Create$WP$Dest